Title : 7th Golden Rooster Awards
Text : '''The 7th Golden Rooster Awards''' honoring the best in mainland China film of 1987, was given in [[Beijing]].<ref>[http://ent.163.com/09/0902/21/5I822IHR00033JNV.html 《芙蓉镇》:反思文化大革命伤痛的高峰力作] 163.com September 02, 2009</ref>

